short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Amazing rotating Dogs theme new tab and clock for your browser

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Change the background image on new tabs to feature cool Dogs and Dogs related images! The extension also provides users with a Custom Web Search on the New Tab.

By installing "Dogs Tab" extension, you agree to the EULA and Privacy Policy, and to set your new tab page to Dogs Background.

The search results used within the extension will be provided by Microsoft Bing. However, the extension will not make any changes in your default browser search setting.

Free stock media content is distributed by Unsplash - https://unsplash.com

Privacy Policy: https://dogstab.xyz/Privacy-Policy.html
